---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
// Services page per PRD section 5.2
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Projexions"
  description="Projexions provides flexible bookkeeping and financial support tailored to the needs of each business. Engagements range from short-term cleanup and project work to ongoing monthly support."
  currentPath="/services"
>
  <div class="page-container">
    <h1 class="serif-heading text-4xl font-semibold mb-6 text-center">Services</h1>

    <div class="services-card">
      <div class="prose-content">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Tax Season Bookkeeping Readiness</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For businesses approaching tax season with uncertainty, Projexions offers a structured, one-time evaluation.
        </p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>60-minute bookkeeping evaluation call</li>
          <li>High-level evaluation of QuickBooks or equivalent systems</li>
          <li>Identification of record gaps and filing blockers</li>
          <li>Written <strong>Tax Readiness Map (PDF)</strong> delivered within 48 hours</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This service does not include cleanup, corrections, tax advice, or filing.<br>
          Its purpose is to provide clarity before engaging a CPA or committing to additional work.
        </p>

        <div class="section-cta" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/tax-season-bookkeeping-readiness" class="btn-primary">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Bookkeeper Hiring Help</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hiring the wrong bookkeeper can lead to months of cleanup, confusion, and avoidable cost.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Projexions offers <strong>Bookkeeper Hiring Help</strong> for businesses that want a second opinion before making a hire.
        </p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>Review of role context and responsibilities</li>
          <li>Review of interview notes or a recorded interview</li>
          <li>Written risk summary identifying:
            <ul class="resource-list text-lg ml-6">
              <li>competency signals</li>
              <li>red flags</li>
              <li>areas to verify before hiring</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="section-cta" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request Hiring Help</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-center">
          <strong>Fee:</strong> $250<br>
          <strong>Delivery:</strong> 24–48 hours
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 text-center">
          This service does not include hiring decisions, HR advice, or guarantees.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Bookkeeping Services</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Projexions provides hands-on bookkeeping services on a limited, case-by-case basis.
        </p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>Short-term cleanup or catch-up work</li>
          <li>Stabilization ahead of tax filing or CPA evaluation</li>
          <li>Limited ongoing support where scope is clearly defined</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Bookkeeping engagements are scoped individually based on complexity, timing, and fit.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Scope & Boundaries</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Projexions provides organization and clarity, not professional advice.
        </p>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>No tax advice or tax filing</li>
          <li>No accounting opinions or audits</li>
          <li>No legal or financial advice</li>
          <li>No guarantees of outcomes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .section-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
